cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.DS, cs.AI

The paper introduces a new clustering algorithm that is particularly effective for data with nonconvex or manifold structure, such as images or text. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Among these, cs.LG is the most likely category as the paper focuses on the optimization algorithm used in the clustering process.
